                Atomic Energy (Soviet Union)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1949-09-27/debates/e519531e-4fe6-4c7d-84d3-c2d452e3eb4a/DetainedBritishSoldiers(Berlin)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
